milestones.description: Jayasuriya and Russel Arnold's 166-run partnership is SL's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 139 between Duleep Mendis and de Silva
Sri Lanka's 246-run win against India is the largest margin of victory in terms of runs in ODIs, beating 191-run win against Zimbabwe
Jayasuriya's 189 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for SL), surpassing Jayasuriya's 151
